version_description:
Watercolor Logo Maker 2.0 is here!

Big Art Update! All artwork and watercolors have been refreshed and hand painted one by one:

• All new logo styles with texture and multicolor variations!
• All new artwork in full color with shading!
• All new fresh watercolors!
• All new fonts!

Working on some more updates for you. If you like the update please leave a review :)

Fixes an issue with In-App Purchases that affected a few users. If you find a bug please contact support@tapflatapps.com and we’ll look into it right away.

Like the app? Please help us by leaving a review in the App Store :)
